WEBVTT

00:00.822 --> 00:02.451
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:02.452 --> 00:05.141
I'm Rebekah Mikaelson!

00:05.142 --> 00:06.615
Ruben: A witch named
Eva Sinclair

00:06.616 --> 00:09.232
was stealing children
to channel their power.

00:09.233 --> 00:10.656
It doesn't matter
what she's done.

00:10.657 --> 00:12.547
I've still appropriated
her body without her consent.

00:12.548 --> 00:14.679
The wolves need a new leader.

00:14.680 --> 00:19.205
I can help you become the leader
your pack deserves.

00:19.206 --> 00:22.509
Josephine: The treme coven wants
Vincent Griffith returned.

00:24.651 --> 00:26.886
Agh!

00:26.887 --> 00:28.399
Who are you?

00:28.400 --> 00:30.035
Elijah: Vincent Griffith
is alive and free

00:30.036 --> 00:32.058
from the influence
of my brother Finn.

00:32.058 --> 00:35.245
If I have woken from my slumber,
then Dahlia has, as well.

00:35.246 --> 00:37.129
Once she's sensed
your child's magic,

00:37.130 --> 00:38.690
she will come for her.

